Title: Relates to notifying counties of any relocation program established by another social services district
Summary: Relates to notifying counties of any relocation program established by another social services district; requires social services districts that have established such a program to annually report to the office of temporary and disability assistance.
LawCode: Amd ยง62, Soc Serv L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the social services law, in relation to notifying counties of any relocation program established by another social services district
